CAMERUPT has a volcano inside its body.
Magma of 18,000 degrees F courses
through its body. Occasionally, the humps on this
POKMONs back erupt, spewing the
superheated magma.

formed by a transformation of its
bones. They sometimes blast out molten magma. This POKMON apparently erupts
often when it is enraged.
